data.description: Custom built home finished in 2004. The roof was replaced with a metal type in 2013. A/C is less than 1 year old. Screened porch.   The property has large (17'x30') RV storage with double roll-up doors, and a storage pod turned into a barn (16'x40'). There is a 1bd/1bh unit attached to the storage barn, that with some work can be turned into a nice apartment.
